I like this one! I feel like at the end we're supposed to assume that the figures did something bad to him (?) but i prefer to read it as the story of a bunch of strange beings (maybe sharing a collective conscious) that just really liked Elvis, and are trying to preserve his memory :( Is there a  way to interpret these? Who knows.

Anyway, love the concept in general of an elvis impersonator SCP. Or eldritch and creepily obsessed Elvis fans or whatever this is.







